---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Admin Setup">
  <main class="section narrow">
    <p class="eyebrow">Admin setup</p>
    <h1>GitHub + Cloudflare Pages Admin</h1>
    <p>
      This project uses Sveltia CMS for the private input dashboard. Content is saved to GitHub, and Cloudflare Pages rebuilds the public website after each save.
    </p>
    <div class="card mt-4">
      <h2>Setup checklist</h2>
      <ol class="rich-list">
        <li>Upload the project to GitHub.</li>
        <li>Edit <code>public/admin/config.yml</code> and set <code>repo</code> to your GitHub username/repo.</li>
        <li>Deploy the repository on Cloudflare Pages.</li>
        <li>Open <code>/admin</code> and sign in with a GitHub token.</li>
        <li>Add profile, projects, screenshots, certificates, documents, resume, and posts.</li>
      </ol>
      <p>Full instructions are in <code>CLOUDFLARE_GITHUB_ADMIN_SETUP.md</code>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
